The subject of this essay is a management course for the tile industry, which uses software as an education tool. It is indicated for users without experience in the sector, with minimum knowledge, to make the incorporation to this kind of enterprise and the carrying out of the job possible, not being necessary a specific formation. This course is based on the navigation between menus, and it allows the task to be done, acceding to the incorporated items, in a fast and easy way. The administration department can receive a great assistance since all the data that is introducted in each module is accessible from the rest of the modules, so that the information can be brought up to date all the time. The code that it has been done in is the RPG code.